{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-archive-js","path":"/archive/","result":{"data":{"posts":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"21534246-1856-5fea-ab36-104043a2b56e","publishedAt":"2021-02-16T04:00:00.000Z","mainImage":{"crop":null,"hotspot":null,"asset":{"_id":"image-1f3be06cf239b485c7a7e78dc937e22484d220be-640x480-png"},"alt":"ming-wen-chun-qiu"},"title":"李锐：这段历史是很重要的","_rawExcerpt":[{"_key":"af2ad76bd56b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"af2ad76bd56b0","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"编者按"},{"_key":"af2ad76bd56b1","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"：今天是华国锋诞辰100周年。我的挚友、中国当代史学者施滨海先生在因故去世前，留下来一部未及出版的书稿《历史转折中的华国锋》，李锐先生生前为此书作了序言。现把这篇序言转发在这里，作为对华国锋先生，对这本书的作者和序者，对今天这个日子的纪念。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"slug":{"current":"zhe-duan-li-shi"}}},{"node":{"id":"00f3df48-869a-54a9-b336-f14f870438b6","publishedAt":"2020-08-18T03:00:00.000Z","mainImage":{"crop":null,"hotspot":null,"asset":{"_id":"image-1f3be06cf239b485c7a7e78dc937e22484d220be-640x480-png"},"alt":"min-wen-chun-qiu"},"title":"邓小平《党和国家领导制度改革》的讲话","_rawExcerpt":[{"_key":"01d58f884962","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"01d58f8849620","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"1980年8月18日，邓小平在中共中央政治局扩大会议上做了一篇讲话，对中国政治体制中的“权力过分集中”的弊端进行了严厉批判，首次提出了“党和国家领导制度改革”的问题。这篇讲话，后来被中共十三大尊为“中国政治体制改革的纲领性文献”，也被党内外的主流研究者们奉为研究邓小平政治体制改革思想的经典。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"slug":{"current":"dxp-dang-guojia-zhidu-gaige"}}},{"node":{"id":"ba7a842e-8327-540f-b5f5-37bc97f27b86","publishedAt":"2020-08-17T03:00:00.000Z","mainImage":{"crop":null,"hotspot":null,"asset":{"_id":"image-1f3be06cf239b485c7a7e78dc937e22484d220be-640x480-png"},"alt":"min-wen-chun-qiu"},"title":"反封建专制里程碑：邓小平“八一八”讲话","_rawExcerpt":[{"_key":"8243b3e79acb","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"8243b3e79acb0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"25年前的8月18日，邓小平在政治局扩大会议上作了一个意义重大的讲话：《党和国家领导制度的改革》。在这个重要讲话中，邓小平分析了我们党和国家领导制度的种种弊端，如：官僚主义现象，突出表现为高高在上、滥用权力、脱离实际、脱离群众、思想僵化、墨守成规、不负责任、不守信用、压制民主、欺上瞒下、专横跋扈、贪赃枉法等等；"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"slug":{"current":"fan-feng-jian-dxp-81"}}},{"node":{"id":"dab23e8e-f924-56f9-911b-0a1b0d5a4af9","publishedAt":"2020-07-05T03:00:00.000Z","mainImage":{"crop":null,"hotspot":null,"asset":{"_id":"image-1f3be06cf239b485c7a7e78dc937e22484d220be-640x480-png"},"alt":"国史札记"},"title":"评《国史札记》兼论高饶事件","_rawExcerpt":[{"_key":"54417e8a0d42","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"54417e8a0d420","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"林蕴晖教授的著作《国史札记·事件篇》，大量利用了近年来公布的新史料，以新的史观方法，钩沉梳理了建国以来党史上的一系列重大事件，以个人的独立研究，剔抉发微，廓清了一些历史之谜，于历史研究中给人们以现实的思考，可称为是中国当代史研究中不断推陈出新的扛鼎之作。阅读该书，可对学界的中国当代史梳理工作一窥端倪。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"slug":{"current":"guo-shi-zha-ji"}}},{"node":{"id":"7bcc8d09-6809-512b-9d50-27aa83e9bc96","publishedAt":"2019-04-08T22:00:00.000Z","mainImage":{"crop":{"_key":null,"_type":"sanity.imageCrop","top":0.42778306115423054,"bottom":0,"left":0.04426787741203178,"right":0.5039727582292847},"hotspot":{"_key":null,"_type":"sanity.imageHotspot","x":0.2701475595913736,"y":0.7138915305771152,"height":0.5722169388457694,"width":0.4517593643586836},"asset":{"_id":"image-26310230bf276b6456ba36e2e232a9c7ae154b8e-1350x900-png"},"alt":"Person standing in a field of sunflowers"},"title":"Exploration powered by structured content","_rawExcerpt":[{"_key":"bdfbfa656915","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"bdfbfa6569150","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Structured content as fuel for creative exploration of new technology."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"slug":{"current":"exploration-powered-by-structured-content"}}},{"node":{"id":"d8d262e3-d9ec-5c17-ac98-e96859185672","publishedAt":"2018-11-14T23:00:00.000Z","mainImage":{"crop":null,"hotspot":null,"asset":{"_id":"image-6b890fc3902645a75a82c95e18ae6c309c77bab3-1350x900-png"},"alt":"Person holding a smart phone"},"title":"A CMS I Can use on My Phone. Finally!","_rawExcerpt":[{"_key":"c7590624e000","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c7590624e0000","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Less of a hassle when you're out and about and want to fix something quickly."}],"mar